{"about_the_game":"Get ready for <strong>a new experience on Windows desktop and VR</strong>, <br>where you get to build your ultimate racing machine, tailored to your driving style and optimized for performance, or race to the finish line with a monster what <strong>makes you smile.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320470/extras/5.gif?t=1688245392\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320470/extras/3.gif?t=1688245392\" /><br><br>Take on thrilling <strong>challenges to unlock</strong> a wide range of tracks, cars, and wheels. <br>And here's the best part: this is just the beginning! You can <strong>expect regular updates</strong> featuring fresh challenges, exciting tracks, and cool cars. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320470/extras/1.gif?t=1688245392\" /><br><br>Play the demo and if you like the game don't miss out on the <strong>special early access price</strong> as the game continues to grow and evolve!<br><br>With <strong>stylised graphics and arcade-like physics</strong>, every turn, straightway and ramp will put your skills to the test. <br><strong>Feel the thrill of the race like never before in VR</strong>, as you immerse yourself counting the seconds on the home stretch.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320470/extras/4.gif?t=1688245392\" /><br><br>The game features:<br>- Challenge unlock system: complete challenges to unlock cars, wheels, levels<br>- Game modes: race against your ghost and beat your best lap or race against AI opponents<br>- Garage: customize your car<br><br>Coming soon:<br>- UX improvements<br>- New level and challenges<br>- New cars and addons<br>- New game modes<br><br>So what are you waiting for? Get behind the wheel and start building your car today. <